      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Wiktionary|bell curve}}

'''Bell curve''' can refer to:

* A [[Gaussian function]], a specific kind of function whose graph is a bell-shaped curve
* [[Normal distribution]], whose density function graph is a bell-shaped curve
* ''[[The Bell Curve]]'', a book by Richard J. Herrnstein and Charles Murray
* [[Bell curve grading]], a method of evaluating scholastic performance

