* Goldwater, Barry. ''Goldwater'' (1988) ISBN 0-385-23947-5, autobiography

==Relatives==
Goldwater's nephew, [[Don Goldwater]], sought the [[Arizona Republican Party]] nomination for [[Governor of Arizona]] in 2006, but was defeated by [[Len Munsil]]. Munsil was in turn defeated by [[Janet Napolitano]], who was re-elected, and who, in 2009, became [[Secretary of Homeland Security]].

