 |starring = {{Unbulleted list|[[Bruce Boxleitner]]|[[Michael O'Hare]]|[[Claudia Christian]]|[[Jerry Doyle (Actor)|Jerry Doyle]]|[[Mira Furlan]]|[[Richard Biggs]]|[[Andrea Thompson]]|[[Bill Mumy]]|[[Jason Carter (actor)|Jason Carter]]|[[Tracy Scoggins]]|[[Stephen Furst]]|[[Patricia Tallman]]|[[Peter Jurasik]]|[[Andreas Katsulas]]|[[Robert Rusler]] |  
