{{Other uses}}
{{Infobox Organization
|name         = Black Hand
|image        = Blackhandcockade.jpg
|size         = 200px
|motto        = ''Freedom or Death; Unity or Death; Death of Tyranny!''
|formation    = May 9, 1911
