*The [[Balkans Campaign (World War I)|Balkan campaigns]] of [[World War I]] (1914–1918)
*The [[Balkans Campaign|Balkan campaigns]] of [[World War II]] (1940–1945)
*The [[Yugoslav wars]] (1991–1999)
* [[Persecution of Muslims]]

