      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Refimprove|date=August 2009}}  {{Infobox Beverage
|name         = Bombay Sapphire
|image        = [[Image:Bombay-sapphire.jpg|80px]]
|type         = [[Gin]]
|abv          = 47.0% (US)&lt;br /&gt;40% (UK)
|proof        = 94
|manufacturer = Bombay Spirits Co., Ltd.
|distributor  = [[Bacardi]]
|origin       = [[England]]
|introduced   = 1987
|discontinued =
